						               													<description>CAMPAIGNS OF DEATH&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HARDCOVER CAMPAIGN BOOK!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A hardcover book that has refined rules and guidelines for creating custom campaigns from the core game and our 12 current expansions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Includes 3 x 30 Lantern year campaigns, each with their own timelines, and a sprinkle of unique innovations, story events,&amp;#10;settlement events, and new gear.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Also includes 2, 3-5 lantern year short format campaigns.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;These campaigns will serve as examples of our new node system&amp;#10;and help teach you how to build your own campaigns, where its&amp;#10;appropriate to shift timeline events to prevent overcrowding, how to keep the difficulty balanced at the KD level and when is ok to add a boon type story event (like Hands of Heat).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Includes details about the nodes and power levels of all the current monsters (from the core game to the currently released expansions *NOT NEW EXPANSIONS).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Also includes my personal take on creating custom campaigns.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Content Pitch:&amp;#10;l x Hard cover Book (Est. 60-100 Pages)&amp;#10;1 X Ancient Butcher Monster (50mm or 100mm base)&amp;#10;3 x New Hybrid Armor Set Narrative Sculpts&amp;#10;80 x Game Cards&amp;#10;10 X Gear Cards&amp;#10;3 x campaign Specific Settlement Record Pads&amp;#10;1 x Blank Settlement Record Pad&amp;#10;2 x Character Record Pads&amp;#10;Generous Fistful of new Story Events!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
